{"tid":722313,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Vivo 3D超感應技術","createTime":"2018-06-29T11:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T14:50:23.000Z","uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4da33acd2f50e3966045b244de8831e551363fb1","tid":722313,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"Vivo剛於上海MWC上發佈了TOF 3D超感應技術，似要和iPhone X的TrueDepth一較高下。早前Vivo搶先用上屏幕指紋識別，近日Vivo和OPPO都分別推出了升降式鏡頭實現真全屏幕設計，國產廠商技術似乎越來越激進。<br />\n<br />\nTOF全稱Time Of Flight，即透過光的反射時間得知物體的距離，與FaceID使用的TrueDepth技術類似，不過Vivo的規格上就完全超越FaceID。TOF 3D共用上30萬個偵測點，比FaceID的3萬點多十倍，而偵測距離達3米，較FaceID遠3倍。偵測點越多，獲得的細節也就更多，可以說是更加安全。<br />\n現場有工程機供使用，記者實試掃描3D頭像，可能因為現場燈光複雜，彩色3D頭像比較詭異，但整個3D頭像的髮型、臉型和五官細節都很不錯，相信此技術再經調教後會有更好的效果。目前工程機已有人像光效、整容等的應用，而微信也已支援此人臉識別支付。雖然此技術可以應用的地方有很多，但Vivo自己都已經去除了M字額，難道要倒退才能放下這組鏡頭？<br />\n<br />\n現場也展示了目前有水貨到港的Vivo NEX，規格不再詳述，主要講一下大家最關心的升降式相機。鏡頭彈出的速度很快，不會影響相機使用體驗，而官方也表示升降5萬次都沒有問題。記者試過用力屈曲鏡頭，鏡頭都完全沒有晃動，而且鏡頭有彈力緩衝，太大力的話就會自動縮回，耐用性算是不錯，最大的缺點就是不防塵防水了。<br />\n雖然Vivo NEX的升降結構有缺點，但已是目前最好的全屏幕設計方向。希望這些激進的國產廠商會刺激到其他國際大廠，拿出更加激進的技術和設計，到時就是消費者得益了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/193253_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F193253_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2a49394f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/193256_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F193256_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d4e2e7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/193258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F193258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e47812e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91606f85077f18408f2b9974e2a4d026a62cb605","tid":722313,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T11:41:41.000Z","msg":"勁過iphone X<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163c94a6ea42f00f60314f44670422501dac8937","tid":722313,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"其實勁過都唔出奇 話晒iphone x果個已經係上年既技術"},{"pid":"39fb4e5019f4f008c9e339a0e9044bab69e0f01d","tid":722313,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"科技一定係不斷進步，樂見各廠推陳出新"},{"pid":"7c668c87256874de64158aea5fdc38bb106c6e06","tid":722313,"uid":10717,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"買sony既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094ad2673343c771bc562dbf960f04198fa3c17a","tid":722313,"uid":164092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c668c87256874de64158aea5fdc38bb106c6e06","tid":722313,"uid":10717,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"買sony既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"Sony Mobile<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcdde9ee4956176c13889ae161341116270eece","tid":722313,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"大陸人真係7閪到無人有，屌你老母買返嚟當係自己技術"},{"pid":"a107d54a1fe483922471aa67c67848b0f036ea37","tid":722313,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c66